NEON Source tree
================

Here's an overview of the source tree:

	doc/ - User and Developer documentation
	man/ - Man page sources
	src/ - Actual source code of NEON.
	COPYING.SHA1 - Copyright/License for the SHA1 Library
	COPYRIGHT - Copyright/License information
	HACKING - Contributing information
	IDEAS - Random ideas for NEON
	INSTALL - Installation Information
	Makefile - The top-level Makefile for NEON
	README - The project README file
	TREE - This file
	TASKS - NEON's todo list
